      "description": "Applicability is restricted to non-cannulated titanium alloy pedicle screws with nominal diameter 7.5 mm and shank length 45–55 mm, tested under quasi-static ASTM F1717 compression-bending at crosshead displacement rates ≤5 mm/min. Results are not applicable to cannulated variants, dynamic fatigue loading, or screw diameters outside 7.0–8.0 mm."
    },
